data.description: A perfect hideout in dwntwn Old Bisbee. Up 64 stairs, at the end of the sidewalk. Very little walking traffic ...if any. Private Courtyard with a huge pine tree, storage room, and outdoor furniture. Kitchen and Living space upstairs, with fantastic views. Spiral staircase downstairs, has 1 bedroom, 1 bath and laundry room. Both upstairs and downstairs have exits to the courtyard. All furnishings convey, with exception of personals. Move in ready. No designated parking. Available street parking.
